<td style="padding:0px; border-top:solid 1px #aaaaaa;">
<div style="text-align:right"><span class="noprint plainlinks navbar" style=""><span style="">This box:</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;word-spacing:-.12em;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Belarusians" title="Template:Belarusians"><span style="" title="View this template">view</span></a> <span style=""><b>·</b></span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Belarusians&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Belarusians (page does not exist)"><span style="" title="Discuss this template">talk</span></a> <span style=""><b>·</b></span> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Belarusians&amp;action=edit" class="external text" rel="nofollow"><span style="" title="Edit this template">edit</span></a></span></span></div>
